---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Regê Engenharia | Projetos, Construção e Regularização de Obras"
  description="A Regê Engenharia é especializada em gerenciamento de obras chave na mão, projetos arquitetônicos e estruturais e regularização completa de imóveis em Navegantes - SC."
  showHeader={false}
  showFooter={false}
>

<!-- ══ NAV ══ -->
<nav class="v2-nav" id="v2-nav">
  <div class="v2-nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="v2-logo">
      <span class="v2-logo-mark">R</span>
      <span class="v2-logo-text">REGÊ <em>ENGENHARIA</em></span>
    </a>
    <ul class="v2-nav-links">
      <li><a href="#v2-sobre">Sobre</a></li>
      <li><a href="#v2-servicos">Serviços</a></li>
      <li><a href="#v2-portfolio">Portfólio</a></li>
      <li><a href="#v2-depoimentos">BLOG</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="https://bitlybr.net/rege" class="v2-nav-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      Fale Conosco
    </a>
    <button class="v2-hamburger" id="v2-hamburger" aria-label="Menu">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="v2-mobile-menu" id="v2-mobile-menu">
    <a href="#v2-sobre">Sobre</a>
    <a href="#v2-servicos">Serviços</a>
    <a href="#v2-portfolio">Portfólio</a>
    <a href="#v2-depoimentos">BLOG</a>
    <a href="https://bitlybr.net/rege" class="v2-mobile-cta" target="_blank">Fale Conosco</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
<section class="v2-hero" id="v2-hero">
  <div class="v2-hero-bg">
    <img src="/images/hero-rege.png" alt="Obra Regê Engenharia" />
    <div class="v2-hero-overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="v2-hero-lines" aria-hidden="true">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="v2-hero-content">
    <div class="v2-hero-badge">
      <span class="v2-badge-dot"></span>
      NAVEGANTES · SC · DESDE 2016
    </div>
    <h1 class="v2-hero-title">
      <span class="v2-title-line" style="animation-delay:0.3s">PROJETANDO</span>
      <span class="v2-title-line v2-title-accent" style="animation-delay:0.45s">ESPAÇOS,</span>
      <span class="v2-title-line" style="animation-delay:0.6s">CONSTRUINDO</span>
      <span class="v2-title-line v2-title-stroke" style="animation-delay:0.75s">SONHOS.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="v2-hero-sub">
      Da concepção à chave na mão — engenharia de excelência,
      transparência absoluta e resultado que supera expectativas.
    </p>
    <div class="v2-hero-actions">
      <a href="https://bitlybr.net/rege" class="v2-btn v2-btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span>Iniciar Projeto</span>
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m5 12 14 0"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#v2-portfolio" class="v2-btn v2-btn-ghost">Ver Portfólio</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="v2-hero-scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="v2-scroll-line"></div>
    <span>SCROLL</span>
  </div>
  <div class="v2-hero-stats">
    <div class="v2-stat">
      <strong class="v2-stat-num" data-count="8">0</strong><span class="v2-stat-suf">+</span>
      <p>Anos</p>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="v2-stat">
      <strong class="v2-stat-num" data-count="45">0</strong><span class="v2-stat-suf">+</span>
      <p>Obras</p>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="v2-stat">
      <strong class="v2-stat-num" data-count="15">0</strong><span class="v2-stat-suf">k m²</span>
      <p>Gerenciados</p>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="v2-stat">
      <strong class="v2-stat-num" data-count="100">0</strong><span class="v2-stat-suf">%</span>
      <p>Satisfação</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ ABOUT ══ -->
<section class="v2-about" id="v2-sobre">
  <div class="v2-container">
    <div class="v2-about-grid">
      <div class="v2-about-img v2-reveal">
        <div class="v2-img-frame">
          <img src="/images/sobre-nos.png" alt="Equipe Regê Engenharia" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="v2-about-badge-float">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m2 22 9.6-9.6"/><path d="m17 7-2.5 2.5"/><path d="M14.5 2 22 9.5l-7 7L7.5 9l7-7z"/></svg>
          <div>
            <strong>Chave na Mão</strong>
            <span>Processo 100% gerenciado</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-about-text v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="v2-eyebrow">QUEM SOMOS</span>
        <h2 class="v2-section-title">Engenharia com<br /><em>propósito real.</em></h2>
        <div class="v2-title-underline"></div>
        <p class="v2-about-lead">A Regê Engenharia nasceu com o objetivo de materializar projetos de forma transparente, técnica e sofisticada.</p>
        <p class="v2-about-body">Com sede em Navegantes - SC, somos especializados no gerenciamento de obras residenciais e comerciais no modelo <strong>chave na mão (turnkey)</strong>. Cuidamos de cada etapa do processo construtivo: desde os estudos preliminares, modelagem de projetos integrados, orçamento executivo detalhado até a execução técnica no canteiro e a entrega das chaves.</p>
        <div class="v2-pillars">
          <div class="v2-pillar">
            <div class="v2-pillar-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><h4>Transparência</h4><p>Relatórios financeiros claros e controle rígido.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-pillar">
            <div class="v2-pillar-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><h4>Qualidade</h4><p>Materiais certificados e mão de obra qualificada.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-pillar">
            <div class="v2-pillar-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><h4>Pontualidade</h4><p>Cumprimento rigoroso dos prazos acordados.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-pillar">
            <div class="v2-pillar-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><h4>Dedicação</h4><p>Atendimento personalizado e próximo ao cliente.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ SERVICES ══ -->
<section class="v2-services" id="v2-servicos">
  <div class="v2-services-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="v2-container">
    <div class="v2-section-header v2-reveal">
      <span class="v2-eyebrow v2-eyebrow-light">CONFIANÇA E EXCELÊNCIA</span>
      <h2 class="v2-section-title v2-light">Serviços &amp;<br /><em>Soluções</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-services-grid">
      <div class="v2-svc-card v2-svc-featured v2-reveal">
        <div class="v2-svc-num">01</div>
        <div class="v2-svc-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="7.5" cy="15.5" r="5.5"/><path d="m21 3-9.6 9.6"/><path d="m15.5 7.5 3 3"/><path d="m18.5 4.5 3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Da Concepção à Chave na Mão</h3>
        <p>Cuidamos de todo o processo da sua obra, desde os primeiros esboços arquitetônicos e modelagem 3D até a limpeza pós-obra e a entrega final das chaves. Tranquilidade absoluta para você.</p>
        <div class="v2-svc-tag">TURNKEY</div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-svc-card v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="v2-svc-num">02</div>
        <div class="v2-svc-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 22V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v18"/><path d="M10 6h4"/><path d="M10 10h4"/><path d="M8 14h8"/><path d="M8 18h8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Projetos Personalizados</h3>
        <p>Projetos de arquitetura, design de interiores, cálculo estrutural e instalações integrados sob medida para o seu estilo de vida.</p>
        <div class="v2-svc-tag">PROJETOS</div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-svc-card v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="v2-svc-num">03</div>
        <div class="v2-svc-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><circle cx="10" cy="15" r="2"/><path d="m11.5 16.5 3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Aprovações e Regularizações</h3>
        <p>Aprovação junto à Prefeitura, licenciamento do Corpo de Bombeiros, averbações e regularização completa de registros de imóveis.</p>
        <div class="v2-svc-tag">LEGAL</div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-svc-card v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="v2-svc-num">04</div>
        <div class="v2-svc-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 22h20"/><path d="M16 22V2h-4v20"/><path d="M12 5h8"/><path d="M12 9h8"/><path d="M8 22V10H4v12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Execução &amp; Gestão de Obras</h3>
        <p>Gestão técnica rigorosa do canteiro. Fidelidade ao projeto, prazos cumpridos, controle financeiro transparente e segurança estrutural máxima.</p>
        <div class="v2-svc-tag">EXECUÇÃO</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ QUOTE BANNER ══ -->
<div class="v2-quote-banner">
  <div class="v2-container">
    <blockquote>
      <span class="v2-quote-mark">"</span>Da concepção à chave na mão, nós estamos com você em cada etapa.<span class="v2-quote-mark">"</span>
    </blockquote>
    <cite>— REGÊ ENGENHARIA</cite>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══ PORTFOLIO ══ -->
<section class="v2-portfolio" id="v2-portfolio">
  <div class="v2-container">
    <div class="v2-section-header v2-reveal">
      <span class="v2-eyebrow">PORTFÓLIO & REALIZAÇÕES</span>
      <h2 class="v2-section-title">Nossos<br /><em>Projetos.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-portfolio-grid">
      <div class="v2-port-card v2-port-large v2-reveal">
        <div class="v2-port-img">
          <img src="/images/obra-residencial.png" alt="Residencial Alto Padrão" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="v2-port-overlay">
            <span class="v2-port-category">OBRA RESIDENCIAL</span>
            <div class="v2-port-info">
              <h3>Residencial Alto Padrão</h3>
              <p>Execução completa com alto nível de detalhamento estrutural.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-port-card v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="v2-port-img">
          <img src="/images/projeto-arquitetonico.png" alt="Projeto Arquitetônico Moderno" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="v2-port-overlay">
            <span class="v2-port-category">PROJETO & ENGENHARIA</span>
            <div class="v2-port-info">
              <h3>Projeto Arquitetônico Moderno</h3>
              <p>Design contemporâneo integrado ao cálculo estrutural.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-port-card v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="v2-port-img">
          <img src="/images/obra-comercial.png" alt="Edifício Comercial Alfa" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="v2-port-overlay">
            <span class="v2-port-category">OBRA COMERCIAL</span>
            <div class="v2-port-info">
              <h3>Edifício Comercial Alfa</h3>
              <p>Construção corporativa com otimização de prazo e controle de insumos.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-port-card v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="v2-port-img">
          <img src="/images/regularizacao.png" alt="Aprovação e Legalização" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="v2-port-overlay">
            <span class="v2-port-category">REGULARIZAÇÃO</span>
            <div class="v2-port-info">
              <h3>Aprovação &amp; Legalização</h3>
              <p>Documentação, habite-se e regularização imobiliária completa.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ TESTIMONIALS ══ -->
<section class="v2-testimonials" id="v2-depoimentos">
  <div class="v2-container">
    <div class="v2-section-header v2-reveal">
      <span class="v2-eyebrow">DEPOIMENTOS DE CLIENTES</span>
      <h2 class="v2-section-title">Quem Confia<br /><em>na Regê.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="v2-testi-grid">
      <div class="v2-testi-card v2-testi-featured v2-reveal">
        <div class="v2-testi-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="v2-testi-text">"A Regê Engenharia construiu a nossa residência do absoluto zero. A transparência no controle de custos e o cumprimento rigoroso dos prazos nos deixaram totalmente tranquilos. A entrega das chaves foi um sonho realizado."</p>
        <div class="v2-testi-author">
          <div class="v2-testi-avatar">MF</div>
          <div><strong>Marcos &amp; Flávia Silveira</strong><span>Cliente Residencial</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-testi-card v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="v2-testi-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="v2-testi-text">"Excelente gestão na execução do nosso galpão comercial. O rigor técnico em toda a estrutura de concreto armado e a organização do canteiro de obras foram exemplares."</p>
        <div class="v2-testi-author">
          <div class="v2-testi-avatar">RM</div>
          <div><strong>Rodrigo Mendes</strong><span>Cliente Comercial</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-testi-card v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="v2-testi-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="v2-testi-text">"Contratamos a Regê para a regularização completa do nosso imóvel e aprovação junto aos Bombeiros. Processo ágil, eficiente e sem burocracia para nós."</p>
        <div class="v2-testi-author">
          <div class="v2-testi-avatar">JR</div>
          <div><strong>Juliana Ramos</strong><span>Regularização Imobiliária</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ CTA FINAL ══ -->
<section class="v2-cta-section">
  <div class="v2-cta-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/images/hero-rege.png" alt="" />
    <div class="v2-cta-overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="v2-container v2-cta-content">
    <span class="v2-eyebrow v2-eyebrow-light">PRONTO PARA COMEÇAR?</span>
    <h2 class="v2-cta-title">Vamos construir<br />o seu sonho juntos.</h2>
    <p class="v2-cta-sub">Entre em contato e receba uma proposta personalizada sem compromisso.</p>
    <a href="https://bitlybr.net/rege" class="v2-btn v2-btn-gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <span>Falar com a Equipe</span>
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m5 12 14 0"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ FOOTER ══ -->
<footer class="v2-footer">
  <div class="v2-container v2-footer-inner">
    <div class="v2-footer-brand">
      <a href="/" class="v2-logo">
        <span class="v2-logo-mark">R</span>
        <span class="v2-logo-text">REGÊ <em>ENGENHARIA</em></span>
      </a>
      <p>Da concepção à chave na mão.<br />Navegantes · SC</p>
    </div>
    <nav class="v2-footer-nav" aria-label="Links do rodapé">
      <h4>Navegação</h4>
      <a href="#v2-sobre">Sobre</a>
      <a href="#v2-servicos">Serviços</a>
      <a href="#v2-portfolio">Portfólio</a>
      <a href="#v2-depoimentos">Depoimentos</a>
    </nav>
    <nav class="v2-footer-nav" aria-label="Contato">
      <h4>Contato</h4>
      <a href="tel:+5547992184100">(47) 99218-4100</a>
      <a href="https://bitlybr.net/rege" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a>
      <a href="mailto:contato@rege.eng.br">contato@rege.eng.br</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="v2-footer-bottom">
    <p>© 2024 Regê Engenharia — Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    <a href="/v1">Versão Original</a>
  </div>
</footer>

</Layout>

<style>
:root {
  --v2-dark: #080e17;
  --v2-dark-2: #0d1520;
  --v2-dark-3: #121c2b;
  --v2-panel: #14202f;
  --v2-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --v2-gold: #c9a84c;
  --v2-gold-2: #e0c06a;
  --v2-gold-muted: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  --v2-cream: #f0ead8;
  --v2-white: #f8f6f1;
  --v2-muted: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
  --v2-font-display: 'Archivo Expanded', sans-serif;
  --v2-font-body: 'Archivo', sans-serif;
  --v2-font-serif: 'Bitter', serif;
  --v2-ease: cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  --v2-ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.0, 0.0, 0.2, 1);
  --v2-radius: 6px;
  --v2-radius-lg: 12px;
}

.v2-container {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
}

/* NAV */
.v2-nav {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  z-index: 1000;
  transition: background 0.4s var(--v2-ease), box-shadow 0.4s var(--v2-ease);
}
.v2-nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(8,14,23,0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  box-shadow: 0 1px 0 var(--v2-border);
}
.v2-nav-inner {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 2.5rem;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
}
.v2-logo {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.v2-logo-mark {
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  background: var(--v2-gold);
  color: var(--v2-dark);
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 4px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.v2-logo-text {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: var(--v2-white);
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.v2-logo-text em {
  display: block;
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--v2-gold);
  font-weight: 400;
}
.v2-nav-links {
  display: flex;
  list-style: none;
  gap: 2rem;
  margin: 0 0 0 auto;
  padding: 0;
}
.v2-nav-links a {
  text-decoration: none;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  transition: color 0.25s;
}
.v2-nav-links a:hover { color: var(--v2-gold); }
.v2-nav-cta {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-dark);
  background: var(--v2-gold);
  padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
  border-radius: 3px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.25s, transform 0.2s;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.v2-nav-cta:hover { background: var(--v2-gold-2); transform: translateY(-1px); }
.v2-hamburger {
  display: none;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 5px;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 4px;
  margin-left: auto;
}
.v2-hamburger span {
  display: block;
  width: 22px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--v2-white);
  transition: all 0.3s;
}
.v2-mobile-menu {
  display: none;
  flex-direction: column;
  background: rgba(8,14,23,0.98);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--v2-border);
}
.v2-mobile-menu a {
  text-decoration: none;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--v2-border);
  transition: color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
}
.v2-mobile-menu a:hover { color: var(--v2-gold); background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05); }
.v2-mobile-cta { color: var(--v2-gold) !important; }
.v2-mobile-menu.open { display: flex; }

/* HERO */
.v2-hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--v2-dark);
}
.v2-hero-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
}
.v2-hero-bg img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  opacity: 0.35;
  filter: grayscale(30%) contrast(1.1);
}
.v2-hero-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(8,14,23,0.95) 45%, rgba(8,14,23,0.3) 100%),
    linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,14,23,0.9) 10%, transparent 50%);
}
.v2-hero-lines {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  display: flex;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.v2-hero-lines span {
  flex: 1;
  border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
}
.v2-hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 10;
  padding: 10rem 1.5rem 6rem;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  width: 100%;
}
.v2-hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-gold);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
  padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 100px;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: v2fadeUp 0.8s var(--v2-ease-out) 0.1s forwards;
}
.v2-badge-dot {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  background: var(--v2-gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: v2pulse 2s infinite;
}
@keyframes v2pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.7); }
}
.v2-hero-title {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin: 0 0 2rem;
  color: var(--v2-white);
}
.v2-title-line {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(30px);
  animation: v2fadeUp 0.8s var(--v2-ease-out) forwards;
}
.v2-title-accent { color: var(--v2-gold); }
.v2-title-stroke {
  -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--v2-white);
  color: transparent;
}
@keyframes v2fadeUp {
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
.v2-hero-sub {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-serif);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
  color: rgba(240,234,216,0.7);
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 560px;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: v2fadeUp 0.8s var(--v2-ease-out) 0.65s forwards;
}
.v2-hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: v2fadeUp 0.8s var(--v2-ease-out) 0.8s forwards;
}
.v2-hero-scroll-hint {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 9rem;
  right: 3rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  z-index: 10;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: v2fadeIn 1s var(--v2-ease) 1.5s forwards;
}
.v2-scroll-line {
  width: 1px;
  height: 60px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--v2-gold), transparent);
  animation: v2scrollLine 2s ease infinite;
}
@keyframes v2scrollLine {
  0% { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: top; }
  50% { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: top; }
  51% { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: bottom; }
  100% { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: bottom; }
}
.v2-hero-scroll-hint span {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.55rem;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: var(--v2-muted);
  writing-mode: vertical-rl;
}
.v2-hero-stats {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  z-index: 10;
  display: flex;
  align-items: stretch;
  background: rgba(8,14,23,0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--v2-border);
  opacity: 0;
  animation: v2fadeIn 0.8s var(--v2-ease-out) 1s forwards;
}
@keyframes v2fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; } }
.v2-stat {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 1.75rem 1rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.v2-stat-num {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--v2-gold);
  line-height: 1;
  display: inline;
}
.v2-stat-suf {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--v2-gold-2);
  margin-left: 2px;
}
.v2-stat p {
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-muted);
  margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
}
.v2-stat-divider {
  width: 1px;
  background: var(--v2-border);
  align-self: stretch;
  margin: 1rem 0;
}

/* BUTTONS */
.v2-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 3px;
  transition: all 0.3s var(--v2-ease);
  cursor: pointer;
}
.v2-btn-primary { background: var(--v2-gold); color: var(--v2-dark); }
.v2-btn-primary:hover { background: var(--v2-gold-2); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(201,168,76,0.35); }
.v2-btn-primary svg { transition: transform 0.3s var(--v2-ease); }
.v2-btn-primary:hover svg { transform: translateX(4px); }
.v2-btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--v2-white); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }
.v2-btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.v2-btn-gold { background: var(--v2-gold); color: var(--v2-dark); font-size: 0.78rem; padding: 1.1rem 2.5rem; }
.v2-btn-gold:hover { background: var(--v2-gold-2); transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(201,168,76,0.4); }
.v2-btn-gold svg { transition: transform 0.3s var(--v2-ease); }
.v2-btn-gold:hover svg { transform: translateX(4px); }

/* EYEBROW */
.v2-eyebrow {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-gold);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.v2-eyebrow-light { color: var(--v2-gold-2); }

/* SECTION TITLE */
.v2-section-title {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.05;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-dark);
  margin: 0;
}
.v2-section-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-serif);
  text-transform: none;
  color: var(--v2-gold);
  letter-spacing: 0;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.v2-section-title.v2-light { color: var(--v2-white); }
.v2-section-header { margin-bottom: 4rem; }

/* REVEAL */
.v2-reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(40px);
  transition: opacity 0.9s var(--v2-ease), transform 0.9s var(--v2-ease);
}
.v2-reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.v2-reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.15s; }
.v2-reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

/* ABOUT */
.v2-about {
  padding: 8rem 0;
  background: var(--v2-white);
  position: relative;
}
.v2-about::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--v2-gold), transparent);
}
.v2-about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
  gap: 6rem;
  align-items: center;
}
.v2-about-img { position: relative; }
.v2-img-frame {
  position: relative;
  aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius-lg);
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(8,14,23,0.2);
}
.v2-img-frame img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.8s var(--v2-ease);
}
.v2-img-frame:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
.v2-img-frame::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 60%, rgba(8,14,23,0.4));
  z-index: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.v2-about-badge-float {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -1.5rem;
  right: -1.5rem;
  background: var(--v2-dark);
  color: var(--v2-white);
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(8,14,23,0.3);
  border: 1px solid var(--v2-border);
  z-index: 2;
}
.v2-about-badge-float svg { stroke: var(--v2-gold); flex-shrink: 0; }
.v2-about-badge-float strong {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  color: var(--v2-white);
}
.v2-about-badge-float span {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--v2-muted);
  display: block;
  margin-top: 0.1rem;
}
.v2-about-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.v2-title-underline {
  width: 50px;
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--v2-gold);
  margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.v2-about-lead {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-serif);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: var(--v2-dark-3);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.v2-about-body {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #555;
  line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.v2-about-body strong { color: var(--v2-dark); font-weight: 700; }
.v2-pillars {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(8,14,23,0.08);
  padding-top: 2rem;
}
.v2-pillar { display: flex; gap: 0.85rem; }
.v2-pillar-icon {
  width: 38px;
  height: 38px;
  background: var(--v2-gold-muted);
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
}
.v2-pillar-icon svg { stroke: var(--v2-gold); }
.v2-pillar h4 {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-dark);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.v2-pillar p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.5; }

/* SERVICES */
.v2-services {
  position: relative;
  padding: 8rem 0;
  background: var(--v2-dark-2);
  overflow: hidden;
}
.v2-services-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 800px 600px at 20% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 600px 400px at 80% 20%, rgba(201,168,76,0.03) 0%, transparent 60%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.v2-services-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
}
.v2-svc-card {
  background: var(--v2-panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--v2-border);
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius-lg);
  padding: 2.5rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: transform 0.4s var(--v2-ease), border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.4s;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.v2-svc-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--v2-gold), transparent);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.4s;
}
.v2-svc-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.2); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(8,14,23,0.4); }
.v2-svc-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
.v2-svc-featured { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.12) 0%, var(--v2-panel) 60%); border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.2); }
.v2-svc-featured::before { opacity: 1; }
.v2-svc-num {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: var(--v2-gold);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  opacity: 0.7;
}
.v2-svc-icon {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  background: var(--v2-gold-muted);
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
}
.v2-svc-card:hover .v2-svc-icon { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.2); transform: scale(1.05); }
.v2-svc-icon svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; stroke: var(--v2-gold); }
.v2-svc-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  color: var(--v2-white);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.v2-svc-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--v2-muted); line-height: 1.8; flex: 1; }
.v2-svc-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-gold);
  background: var(--v2-gold-muted);
  padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
  border-radius: 2px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  align-self: flex-start;
}

/* QUOTE BANNER */
.v2-quote-banner {
  padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  background: var(--v2-gold);
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.v2-quote-banner::before {
  content: '"';
  position: absolute;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-serif);
  font-size: 30rem;
  line-height: 1;
  color: rgba(8,14,23,0.04);
  top: -4rem;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  pointer-events: none;
  user-select: none;
}
.v2-quote-banner blockquote {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-serif);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  color: var(--v2-dark);
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.v2-quote-mark { color: rgba(8,14,23,0.3); }
.v2-quote-banner cite {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: rgba(8,14,23,0.55);
  font-style: normal;
}

/* PORTFOLIO */
.v2-portfolio { padding: 8rem 0; background: var(--v2-white); }
.v2-portfolio-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
  grid-template-rows: auto auto;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}
.v2-port-large { grid-row: span 2; }
.v2-port-card { border-radius: var(--v2-radius-lg); overflow: hidden; }
.v2-port-img {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  min-height: 260px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.v2-port-large .v2-port-img { min-height: 100%; }
.v2-port-img img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.7s var(--v2-ease);
  display: block;
}
.v2-port-card:hover .v2-port-img img { transform: scale(1.07); }
.v2-port-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,14,23,0.88) 25%, rgba(8,14,23,0.15) 70%);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.4s var(--v2-ease);
}
.v2-port-card:hover .v2-port-overlay { opacity: 1; }
.v2-port-category {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-gold);
  background: rgba(8,14,23,0.5);
  padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
  border-radius: 2px;
  align-self: flex-start;
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
}
.v2-port-info {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  transform: translateY(10px);
  transition: transform 0.4s var(--v2-ease);
}
.v2-port-card:hover .v2-port-info { transform: translateY(0); }
.v2-port-info h3 {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-white);
  margin: 0;
}
.v2-port-info p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: rgba(240,234,216,0.7); margin: 0; }

/* TESTIMONIALS */
.v2-testimonials { padding: 8rem 0; background: #f5f2ec; position: relative; }
.v2-testimonials::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--v2-gold), transparent);
}
.v2-testi-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  align-items: start;
}
.v2-testi-card {
  background: var(--v2-white);
  border: 1px solid rgba(8,14,23,0.06);
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius-lg);
  padding: 2.5rem;
